Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Dear Twilight, it is difficult{\i0}\N{\i1} to express how grateful I am{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to you for teaching me the{\i0}\N{\i1} power of friendship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} You would think after more{\i0}\N{\i1} than a thousand years,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} there would be nothing{\i0}\N{\i1} left to learn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} And yet, even a pony as old as{\i0}\N{\i1} I can continue to be surprised{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} by how much there{\i0}\N{\i1} is to know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"I hope you find these\Npostcards enjoyable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I look forward to\Nseeing you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,though I can't say when my\Njourney will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend, Starswirl."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be gratifying to have\Nyour idol writing to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,about the friendship\Nlessons he's learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I'll\Never get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if he really wants\Nto learn about friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he could just come\Nto our school..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Sparkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mail Pony just came\Nwith uh, a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oo! The sewing machines\NI ordered for my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,These came, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.89,0:01:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure what\Nto make of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,These machines were costly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am quite certain\Nthe friendship lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can teach my students with\Nthem will be invaluable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh don't worry, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think of something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't use school\Nfunds to buy these.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the purchase\Nentirely with my own bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that. It's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why waste your time at\Na friendship school
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just a school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn everything they teach and\Nmore at Friendship {\i1}University!?{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would open\Nanother friendship school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh pffft. I'm sure it's nothing\Nto worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Princess\Nof Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What could this other\Nschool possibly offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't just another friendship\Nschool, it's a University!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It says they teach\N"the same lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of competing schools\Nin half the time."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's twice the\Nlearning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's in Las Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If Professor Rarity lets us skip\Nher sewing class -- ROAD TRIP!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we need to\Nlook into this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to judge\Nsolely on appearances,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but.. what kind of\Nfriendship school is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the best friendship\Nschool in the West...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more ponies in here\Nthan at our whole school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is running this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Male voice] Welcome, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You are about to embark on a\Njourney of amazing magnitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,one that will change\Nyour lives forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves to\Nembrace a new path
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and become students of\NFRIENDSHIP U!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Flim and Flam. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ If you're alone and you{\i0}\N{\i1} can't make friends ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ we understand your plight ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Until now there was{\i0}\N{\i1} just one way ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ your friendships could{\i0}\N{\i1} take flight ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ There is a school{\i0}\N{\i1} real far away ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ that'll teach you{\i0}\N{\i1} what to know ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But if you live here{\i0}\N{\i1} you couldn't stay ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ you'd learn you have to gooo.. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Now there is an alternative{\i0}\N{\i1} to all of that adversity ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Not just a school{\i0}\N{\i1} I'll have you know ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But a whole University! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ At Friendship U{\i0}\N{\i1} our aim is true ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ In a city not{\i0}\N{\i1} some backwater ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You'll learn the{\i0}\N{\i1} things you need to know ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ At our new alma mater! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, everypony!\NYou heard correctly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship U, the one and only\NUniversity of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ As you can see we're a{\i0}\N{\i1} success by any kind of stat ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That may be so for all I{\i0}\N{\i1} know but I still smell a rat ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Everypony lookie here that{\i0}\N{\i1} other school's headmare! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Her presence is a testament{\i0}\N{\i1} to the mutual respect we shaaare..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ It really is the final piece{\i0}\N{\i1} to make our work complete ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ To have the{\i0}\N{\i1} Friendship Princess ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ bless our school is{\i0}\N{\i1} such a treat ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Were so honoured!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ At Friendship U{\i0}\N{\i1} we teach to you AND YOU! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ All of our friendship{\i0}\N{\i1} knowledge ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You'll learn it all{\i0}\N{\i1} in half the time ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ at the one and only{\i0}\N{\i1} friendship college ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can anypony learn\Nfriendship in half the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our coursework is\Nso accelerated
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to take longer'd\Nbe a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The lessons that we teach ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Have been reviewed and{\i0}\N{\i1} checked and edited ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Which might explain{\i0}\N{\i1} why our school's about{\i0}\N{\i1} to be accredited ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ At Friendship U{\i0}\N{\i1} Oh yes, it's true ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Even the Princess of{\i0}\N{\i1} Friendship agrees ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The only place in{\i0}\N{\i1} Equestria to give out{\i0}\N{\i1} friendship degrees! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship U!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship U!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship U!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us again why\Nit's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ It's the only University{\i0}\N{\i1} of Friendship U! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Accredited?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It means officially\Nrecognized or authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But who would\Naccredit this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the EEA, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Neighsay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Equestria Educational\NAssociation has taken an
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,interest in institutions\Nthat teach friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in a pony-first environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you didn't\Nthink your school
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,has a monopoly on\Nthe concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she did write\Nthe book on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"How to teach\Nfriendship to {\i1}creatures{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,who will one day use it as\Na weapon against us."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they use\Nfriendship as a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me; it's your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Meantime, this university\Nappears to be a promising option
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for ponies who'd prefer to stick\Nto the EEA book on the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're obviously\Nup to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Flim and Flam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that certainly\Nwasn't.. friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,One would think the headmare\Nof a school of friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,albeit an unaccredited one,\Nwould behave differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless she was trying to\Nundermine the competition? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I... No... What? I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did think the Princess of\NFriendship would be friendlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now fillies\Nand gentlecolts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,let's show the Princess\Njust how friendly we are
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,by signing up for\Nsome classes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I show you around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but approval from\Nthe EEA won't convince me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that this school is\Nwhat you promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And what would it\Ntake to convince you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, somepony who's\Nopinion I respect, for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Somepony like... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Starswirl? What are\Nyou doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, studying friendship at Flim\Nand Flam's wonderful school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know a\Ndisguise when I see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off that\Nridiculous beard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,FLAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.. It-it's really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard rumors\Nyou've returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't believe\Nit until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And if a pony of your\Nstature is studying here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there really isn't anything\Nelse I need to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Chancellor Neighsay,\Nhereby confer upon Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,University complete and\Nunreserved EEA accreditation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you come\Nhere and not my school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My travels brought\Nme to Las Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come for the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but Flim and Flam convinced\Nme to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: You can't\Ntrust Flim and Flam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They tried to con the\NApples out of their farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They sold fake health tonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They run a resort\Nin Las Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, our resort\Nis a legitimate business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent a thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking the worst\Nof a "bad" pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me to look\Nfor the best in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever Flim and\NFlam's past may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,starting this school shows they\Nwant to change for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what's untrustworthy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,about opening a\Nschool of friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even\Ncharge for classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know they're\Nup to something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and until I find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, come\Nto my school instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand feeling\Nthreatened by competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But my word, Princess, I\Nwonder if the ill-manners
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of the creatures at your\Nschool aren't contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I will take my leave\Nbefore I become infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, I promise I'll\Nvisit your school soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but for now, perhaps it's\Nbest if you return there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think they're running\Nan actual friendship school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why we\Nhave to investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't go poking\Naround the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony'll think\NI'm still just
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"threatened by\Nthe competition."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if we do it\Nas.. {\i1}ourselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In these disguises,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we could pass as students\Nat out own school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah. What did I say about\Nusing our real names?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, "Plainity." But\NI'm pretty sure this..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't enough of a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, strangers. Are\Nyou two new here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We sure are. Completely new!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! See you in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I've read enough Shadow\NSpade to know the key to going
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,undercover is rehearsing\Nyour backstory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm "Plainity" and I love\Nbland-old-normal stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No frills for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Heh. Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[groan] My name's Eyepatch.\NI have an eyepatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Per-fect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how do we start\Nour investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You enroll in some classes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and find out what they're\Nactually teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look around and\Nsee what I can find,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,assuming I'm not recognized....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, newest students!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dive right in, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the most important\Nelements of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is being thoughtful,\Ntrue or false?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If by thoughtful you mean\Ngenerous, I'd say true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct! Ha hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a trick question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Very impressive, Ms...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Plainity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well well, Ms. Plainity,\Nkeep it up and you'll be ready
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for our next level in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see if you can\Ndemonstrate for the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's something generous you\Ncould do for me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Class, Plainity here\Nis now my star pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If any of you want a chance\Nat studying with Starswirl,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd take notes on\Nher every action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The door is open, so I'll just\Nassume it's OK to come in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and look around, unless\Nsomepony says it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Element of Laughter\Nand its applications."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, that seems pretty genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"When to support your\Nfriends' decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and when to talk sense."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, that's actually\Nkind of interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ha! "Friendship\NUniversity's true goal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is to help friends\Nbecome better friends?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the proof\Nthat it's all a scam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think an eye\Npatch was enough of a disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we agree that\Neverypony will recognize the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess of Friendship\Nin this photo of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,sneaking into our office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the headline\Nnow, "Princess of Jealousy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle bent on\Nruining her competition!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A news story like that\Nwould destroy your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony will want to go to\Nyour school after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait until the\Npapers get a hold of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Unhinged!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the talk of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, gentleponies, I've\Nfinished another stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The lessons in these worksheets\Nare quite fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight? What's\Ngoing on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just your protégé getting\Ncaught snooping in our office
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in disguise! Well, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh honestly, Princess Twilight,\Nenvy does not look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know these two\Nare up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying\Nto find out what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The only pony I see who's up\Nto something is the pony
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in this picture, and it is\Nnot the Princess I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about to be the\NPrincess all of Equestria knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you decided to drop the whole,\N"uncover the scam" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll rip this silly\Npicture up and not let it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,completely and utterly\Nruin you and your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be generous with\Nall sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gifts, compliments, your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eyepatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your eyepatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Was your cover blown?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Flim and Flam took a picture of\Nme sneaking into their office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Were we wearing our eye patch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't stop investigating,\Nthey're going to tell everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm trying to\Nsabotage their school
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But but but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I am just upset\Nthat Starswirl came here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Flim and Flam may have\Nturned over a new leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you are not\Nthe kind of pony
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to let your emotions\Ncloud your judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think Flim and\NFlam are up to no good,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,even if their lessons\Nreally are impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me. Can you\Nget a message to Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to return\Nthose sewing machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the bits if I'm going\Nto keep advancing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuition's free, but the\Nworksheets sure aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Flim and Flam are\N{\i1}charging{\i0} for these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they have\Nto cover expenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and Flam insists that\Neverything extra
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,goes to improving\Nthe school and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the scam, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These lessons are\Nso valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure I\Ncan't give you more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ah ah! Unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to share them\Nwith a pony like you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is our real reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. And you want to study\Nalongside Starswirl, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back for the rest\Nwhen you can afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'll sell the\Nshirt off my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaand that's the kind of\Ndetermination that'll get you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next level, student\Nwhose.. name I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, maybe I should\Ntake over the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of your reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My reputation isn't worth\Nmuch if I won't risk it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for what I think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, brother of mine, we've got\Nalmost all the bits we need
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to expand our resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we add another level of\Nclasses and worksheets,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should add two\Nlevels, just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's a thing of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what if we added another\Nextreme pool slide here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, as long as the pipes for\Nthe musical chocolate fountain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,go through.. here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: But\Nshouldn't it go closer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to the pudding\Nhot tub {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair point, but-- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew your school was a scam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't the\NPrincess of Jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll be going\Nto the papers after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I suppose I'll just\Nlead your students
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,into this secret room of bits\Nand resort expansion plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Err.. let's not get hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something on us;\Nwe have something on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just call it.. even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can destroy my\Nreputation if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but using your students' bits to\Nexpand your resort is wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,even if the lessons you\Nteach are good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, they're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We copied them from {\i1}your{\i0} book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We just skipped\Nevery other page.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"All the lessons,\Nhalf the time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Fine. If you really\Nwant to call it even,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,give back the bits and stop\Ncharging for my lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can teach them\Nas much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah! Running a school is\Nmore work than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we almost have\Neverything we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Plainity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My star pupil?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Plainity, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to bring\Nsomepony else here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to listen to everything\Nyou just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[mumble] Hey! Starswirl. We\Nwere just about to--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the bits\Nyou've collected from
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,your students and\Nclose your school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[gulp] Yeah. That.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it seems I'll\Nnever stop learning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from your example,\NTwilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a valuable lesson to stand\Nup for what you know is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had known it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for returning our bits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but how are we going to\Nlearn about friendship now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can refer you to a\Nfairly reputable establishment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,just outside of Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite certain the headmare\Nwould consider letting you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Of course, if I ever\Ngo to a school again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure it's yours.\NIn friendship, Starswirl."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't understand\Nhow Flim and Flam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,could have gotten\Na copy of your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. I finished straightening\Nup in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Rarity, I just\Nwanted to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you're definitely\Nkeeping these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's one thing I learned\Nat Friendship University,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not to give up when\Nyou know what's right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know teaching friendship\Nthrough sewing is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to figure out how...
